Title: R version of Python package bubbly (mimick Gapminder visualization tools from Hans Rosling)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: gabi.preda@gmail.com
Description: This package is a R version of bubbly (<a href="https://github.com/AashitaK/bubbly), a Python package    
    for plotting animated and interactive bubble charts using Plotly.
    In order to use it, you will have to call the function rbubbly with the parameters as specified in the example 
    (included with the package).
